DOUBLE B ENTERPRISES, INC., Appellant, v. Thomas E. WHITE, Secretary of the Army, Appellee. No. 01-1593. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. Feb. 12, 2002.

ON MOTION

ORDER

Upon consideration of Double B Enterprises, Inc.’s motion to withdraw its appeal,

IT IS ORDERED THAT:

(1) The motion is granted and this appeal is dismissed.

(2) Each side shall bear its own costs.
